948 font->m_charset.m_chars[i].m_width = CFONT_CALIBRI_144_CHARSET[8*i+2];
949 font->m_charset.m_chars[i].m_height = CFONT_CALIBRI_144_CHARSET[8*i+3];
950 font->m_charset.m_chars[i].m_xOffset = CFONT_CALIBRI_144_CHARSET[8*i+4];
951 font->m_charset.m_chars[i].m_yOffset = CFONT_CALIBRI_144_CHARSET[8*i+5];
952 font->m_charset.m_chars[i].m_xAdvance = CFONT_CALIBRI_144_CHARSET[8*i+6];
953 font->m_charset.m_chars[i].m_page = CFONT_CALIBRI_144_CHARSET[8*i+7];
954 }
955 font->m_charset.preProcess();
956
957 font->m_texture->setImage(std::shared_ptr<chai3d::cImage>(img));
958
959 return (font);
960}
